data.description: First time on market!Custom 4000 sqft brick rambler w/4 car garage & 26x40 RV shop on 1 acre.Natural light throughout this 4 bed 3.5 bath open-concept layout that seamlessly connects entry, living, dining, wet-bar, great room, & kitchen areas for your entertainment needs. Extras include 3 gas/wood fireplaces, automatic house generator, built-ins, heat pump, wide interior doors, custom painted sinks/accents, tropical brick indoor planters, central vac, speaker/intercom & more. Primary bed features 5-piece bath, jetted tub, walk-in closet,& custom slate shower w/waterfall.3 additional beds and generously sized office/den.Outside enjoy 1 acre level lot & covered back patio.26x40 shop features RV hookups/water/clean-out &extra parking on side.
